      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lehigh_Acres%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "By 1997, nearly 90% of Lehigh Acres' lots remained vacant, highlighting a slow growth phase before the 2000s boom.",
